            <title>Data Collection</title>
    
            <introduction>
                <p>
                    First we will work together to generate a data set for our class. We will collect values for three numerical variables.
                    <ol>
                        <li><alert>Height</alert>: your height measured in inches</li>
                        <li><alert>Number of moves</alert>: the number of times you have moved residences</li>
                        <li><alert>Power test score</alert>: your score on the <url href="https://chs.uky.edu/about/news/alum-ny-times-take-30-second-power-test">the 30 second power test</url>.
                            <fn>There are modifications available for this test.</fn></li>
                    </ol>
                </p>
                <p>
                    Enter your data on <url href="https://colostate-my.sharepoint.com/:x:/g/personal/jshrine_colostate_edu/EZAyJvIdrrVDkWq6b7qyztABC72OXclx7KEF4yUi9A9lnQ?e=tHenoi">this shared spreadsheet</url>. 
                    You do not need to include your name.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Copy and paste the data set from the shared spreadsheet to the spreadsheet below. 
                    This copy will be for your individual use for the remainder of the activity.
                </p>
